These are custom actions that I did not include in my trigger lib There is a small flaw in Get First Unfinished Tech function that it can return not null string even if specified object's requirements are all met For example this happen for zerg when you only have Hive, that function will return Hatchery (or Lair if ai has macro hatcheries) as unfinished tech for making Overseer or other Lair or Hatchery tech. This can be "fixed" by instructing AI to build extra Hatchery and Lair too even after making Hive. It seems to also happen for terran when you don't have Command Centers (upgraded them to Orbital/Planetary). Conclusion, in v2.1 I decided to remove Unfinished Tech check.
